Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你好啊  弗萊迪  最近怎樣  -挺好\N- Hey, Freddy! How ya doing? - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好  你這麼說我就安心了\NAll right, that's what I like to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.42,0:01:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-謝了夥計  -改天再聊\N- My man. - Catch you later, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.11,0:03:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《日報》我能聯繫的人都聯繫了\NI spoke to everyone I know at the Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒人告訴我誰給的照片  但肯定是雷米\NNobody's naming sources, but it has to be Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉樂威要出面回應嗎\NIs Galloway going on the record?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會的  他會先和我們接觸\NHe wouldn't. Not without speaking to us first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-最好確保這一點  -我這就去和亞當說\N- Let's be sure about that. - I'll talk to Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許避免和他接觸會更好些\NMaybe it's smarter to avoid contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總得有人出面回應\NSomebody has to respond,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是他就是我們  或者一起回應\Nwhether it's him, or us, or both.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得協調好  小心應對\NWe have to coordinate, and do it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事交給我吧\NLet me take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們先想好了\NWell, let's just think this through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.42,0:04:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會有問題的  弗蘭西斯\NI've got it covered, Francis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那好\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦  還去辦公室嗎\NWhat should I do? Head back to the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你還是在家辦公比較好\NI think you should work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出門的話  很難躲開媒體\NWe can't avoid the press if you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那好  你把好門  -好的  先生\N- All right. You hold down the fort. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你聽克萊爾差遣\NAnd you follow Claire's lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事會解決的  先生\NWe'll shut this down, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能有差池\NThere can't be any doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.33,0:04:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們再過一遍時間線\NLet's walk through a timeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你最初遇見他是什麼時候  -惠特尼雙年展\N- So you first met him when? -In Whitney Biennial...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事傷害了我們兩個人\NThis hurts us both.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要著手去處理的人不是我\NBut it's not my wound to suture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾必須親自動手\NClaire must be the surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.05,0:04:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有她才能穩住局勢\NOnly she can stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裏面有盤子\NYou know we got them plates in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按你要求的改好了\NAll the changes you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多給你5%的追補股份\NGave you five more points on the post-recoupment share.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,營銷宣傳材料需要你認可\NApproval over all the marketing materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀泉旗艦店的人事也要經你認可\NApproval over the staff hires of the flagship in Silver Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-接下來做什麼  -簽字就行\N- So, what next? - You sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:04:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-然後我九萬五就到手了  -這週末吧\N- And I get my $95,000? - By the end of the week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得先把錢從主賬戶注入公司賬戶\NJust have to wire it from our main account into the LLC,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還得核對賬目\Nhad cash years to check for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.73,0:05:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還想給你看看這個\NI want to show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是醬料瓶的樣品\NIt's a mockup of the bottle design.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們已經開始為銀泉店的外觀\NAnd we already started on the concept layouts
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進行概念設計了\Nfor the Silver Spring location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼牆氈都裂開了\NWhy's that linoleum peeling up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追求真實感啊\NTo make it seem real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望比這漂亮些\NI wanted it to look nicer than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可以改掉牆氈的設計\NWe can scratch the peeling linoleum,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不想顯得太高端\Nbut we don't want it to look too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓白人有種體驗下層生活的感覺\NYou want them white folks to feel like they slummin' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是為了營造地道的氣氛\NNo, to have an authentic atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就負責扮演黑鬼\NAnd I get to play the nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪  你也知道這種事\NLook, Freddy, you know how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不只是來吃肋排\NThey don't just want the ribs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是要那種體驗\Nthey want the experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不用出市郊\Nbut without having to leave the suburbs for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是賣燭光晚餐的\NWe're not selling candlelit dinners here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我保證\NBut I promise,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有決策都會經過你的首肯\Nnothing gets built without your signing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我怎麼辦\NSo, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我需要你出面否認  -否認戀情嗎\N- I need you to deny it. - The affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.31,0:06:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戀情  照片  所有這一切\NThe affair, taking the photograph, everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有公開來往的記錄\NWe have a public history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾捐獻作品給...\NI donated work for your...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.75,0:06:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以說那純粹是業務往來\NYou can say we had a business relationship,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你沒有給我拍躺在床上的照片\Nbut that you didn't take the picture of me in the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就說是合成的\NIt was Photoshopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你怎麼說\NWhatever it is you need to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  克萊爾\NI'm so sorry, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只印了一版  還在我這兒呢\NI only have one print and it's still here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個你也得銷毀掉\NYou have to destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.14,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電子文檔也要刪掉\NThe digital file also.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但刪之前先發給我們一份\NBut e-mail us a copy first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得確認照片裏沒有任何痕跡\NWe need to make sure that there's nothing in the image
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聯繫到你的工作室\Nthat links to your studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都聽你的\NWhatever you think is best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.33,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  亞當\NThank you, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時在看\NI watched you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你接受CNN直播採訪的時候\N...when you did the CNN interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本來打定主意不看的  但沒忍住\NI promised myself I wouldn't, but I couldn't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:07:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要因為這種事才說上話真是遺憾\NIt's a shame it takes this for us to talk to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了這事  你還好嗎\NYou're well, besides this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你來過之後\NYeah. I spent three months in Colombia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去哥倫比亞工作了三個月\Nafter you came up here to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實也是逃避\Nbut also to get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到了一個人\NI met someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她來自波哥大\NShe's from Bogota.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.90,0:07:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與當地非政府組織合作\NShe was working with an NGO there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫伊奈茲\NHer name's Inez.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們同居了\NShe's living with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是...\NThat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進展很快\NThings happened quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  確實\NYeah. They did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.98,0:07:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該掛了\NI should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到指示前  我不能和媒體接觸\NSo I won't talk to the press until I get instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.96,0:07:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到你的聲音真好\NIt's good to hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\NYou too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-打完電話了  -嗯\N- You finished? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘋狂\NCrazy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海洛因  可卡因  霹靂可卡因\NSmack, crack, blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  謝謝\NNo, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來點吧  老頭  我們手裏應有盡有\NCome on, old man. We got what you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都不需要\NI don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.78,0:08:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要進門  就得買點\NGotta buy somethin' if you want to get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別擋路\NGet out the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認真的\NFor real.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽的給我滾開\NYou need to get the fuck on outta my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你鬧著玩而已  黑鬼\NJust fucking with you, nigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他媽的冷靜點嘛\NChill the fuck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰\NWho are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.77,0:09:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你爺爺  開門\NYour grandfather. Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎麼辦\NWhat's your plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在家辦公\NWork from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會把鬧劇帶去白宮\NYou don't need me dragging this circus to the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說聲明打算怎麼說\NI mean in terms of a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在起草  力求簡短有力\NWe're drafting one, short and sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  弗蘭克  但我必須得問\NForgive me, Frank, but you know I have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的  我會告訴您的  先生\NIf it were true, I would tell you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要我發表公開聲明嗎\NWould you like me to go on record?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說我支持你...\NSay I stand beside--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  我很感激  總統先生\NNo, no, no. I appreciate that, Mr. President,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但您不該為這種爛事髒了自己的手\Nbut you shouldn't dirty your hands with this sort of garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果媒體逼問\NIf the press corners you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們您不會搬弄是非\Njust tell them you don't engage in gossip mongering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生  嘉樂威先生好像要上電視了\NSir, it seems Mr. Galloway is about to appear on television.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  有需要就告訴我\NGo. Let me know if there's anything I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\NThank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下午好\NGood afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒什麼好說的\NI have very little to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一點  我從沒和克萊爾·安德伍德有過私情\NOnly that I never had any romantic involvement with Claire Underwood,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有拍攝《特區日報》發表的照片\Nand that I did not take the photograph printed in the DC Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.62,0:09:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對副總統夫婦要面對這種\NI'm sorry that the vice president and his wife
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.85,0:09:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荒唐的折磨感到遺憾\Nhave to go through this ridiculous ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:10:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想請媒體不要把我和未婚妻捲入此事\NAnd I would ask that the media leave both my fiancee and me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.06,0:10:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.53,0:10:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小時內能準備好嗎\NYou'll be ready in an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  會準備好的\NYes. We'll be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好換身更...\NYou might want to change into something more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-保守的衣服嗎  -對\N- Conservative? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先放點口風出去\NI'm gonna go throw the hounds a bone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.95,0:10:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這很丟人...\NI know it's demeaning --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許再多說\NNot another word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該更謹慎的\NI should have been more careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.66,0:10:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事就讓它過去吧  就像以前一樣\NWe'll put this behind us, just like we've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我其實也挺希望\NPart of me wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會更介意\NThat you'd be more upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.41,0:10:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克盯上你的原因是我\NTusk came after you because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.04,0:10:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才有資格介意\NIt's you who should be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,浪費精力  對吧\NWasted energy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我倆來說都是\NFor both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要排練一下嗎\NShall we rehearse?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你的幫助\NI don't need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是施捨\NThis ain't a handout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得慢慢還給我  給我打工\NYou have to pay me back over time. Work for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你打工\NWork for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.59,0:11:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何  我都會拿到房子\NI'm gonna get the house either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你住不住  那是你的選擇\NWhether you choose to live in it is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我就需要這個\NYeah, just what I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你坐在安樂椅上\NYou in the easy chair,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次我進門出門都對我冷嘲熱諷\Nlaying into me every time I come in and out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房子是給你和杜肖恩的\NThe place is for you and DeShawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我住我自己的公寓\NI'm gonna be at my own apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.48,0:11:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你確定那黑鬼不是在騙你嗎\NYou sure this nigga ain't just sellin' you smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白紙黑字寫在合同里  怎樣都有九萬五\NSays it right in the contract, 95 Gs no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不確定\NI don't know, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五年沒見\NFive years I don't see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在卻跑過來  說你弄到了九萬五\Nthen you come knocking on the door, talking about you got 95 Gs--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的選擇\NYour choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不想再讓我去監獄裏探視你\NYou didn't want me to visit you no more in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出來之後也不想見...\Nand you sure didn't want to see me after you got out --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不想見你\NI still don't want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經站在這裏了\NWell, here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滾出去  老傢伙\NGet the fuck outta here, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  孩子\NYou listen to me, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直沒什麼可以給你\NI never had nothing to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.16,0:11:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有錢  我有的你也不想要\NI didn't have no money, and you didn't want whatever I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但這可是一棟房子\NBut we talking about a house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.17,0:12:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杜肖恩應該住在一個\NDeShawn deserves to live better
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-比這裏更好的地方  -這不是為了他\N- than in a place like this. - This ain't about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.01,0:12:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了你\NIt's about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道去哪裏找我\NYou know where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見  孩子\NSee you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.41,0:12:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有不到30分鐘\NLess than 30 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要否認嗎\NAre they going to deny?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是讓副總統和夫人自己來說吧\NI'm gonna let the Vice President and his wife speak for themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.76,0:12:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們跟嘉樂威先生有聯絡嗎\NHave they been in contact with Mr. Galloway?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒有\NNo, they haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他們過了一整天才做出回應\NWhy has it taken them a full day to respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你們肯定可以理解\NI'm sure you can understand that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想先就誹謗與污蔑問題\Nthey wanted to consult with legal counsel first
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咨詢法律顧問\Nregarding defamation and slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.90,0:12:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說他們要否認這段婚外情\NYou're saying they will deny the affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說他們30分鐘之內就會出來\NI'm saying they'll be out here in 30 minutes
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們可以引述他們的話而不是我的\Nand you can quote them instead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.65,0:12:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們的耐心\NThank you all very much for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是恨死這個了\NI hate this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  等待嗎\NWhat, waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.73,0:12:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  婚外情  都是狗屁\NNo, the affair. It's bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己像個小報狗仔\NI feel like a tabloid hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.28,0:12:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你寧願整天困在白宮那邊嗎\NYou'd rather be stuck at the White House all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去他的\NFuck this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.12,0:12:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我的寶貴時間做點有意義的事\NTo do something meaningful with my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  幫我訂一張飛往聖路易斯的機票\NHey, I need you to book me a flight to St. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話最好是今晚\NTonight, if you can find something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有問答環節  別費心提問了\NNo Q&A, so don't even try.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請大家規矩一點\NBehave yourselves, people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有人懷疑\NI find it very painful
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對我深愛的丈夫\Nthat anyone would suggest
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.05,0:13:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有不忠行為\NI'm capable of being unfaithful to my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.22,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這讓我感到非常痛心\Nwhom I love dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我與亞當·嘉樂威已相識多年\NI've known Adam Galloway for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.10,0:13:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們都認識他很多年了\NWe both have.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我負責淨水計劃時\NWhen I ran the Clean Water Initiative,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾委託他為營銷活動\NI commissioned him to do a series of photographs
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝一系列攝影作品\Nfor the marketing campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他也極為慷慨地為我們的籌款拍賣會\NAnd he was extremely generous by donating work
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捐贈了自己的作品\Nfor our fund-raising auctions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不知道他為什麼要否認拍攝過這張照片\NSo I'm not sure why he would deny taking the photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡亞當的作品  所以讓他拍了這幅肖像\NI love Adam's work, so I asked him to take this portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.21,0:14:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在這裏拍的  就在這棟房子裏\NWe did it here, at the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.31,0:14:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍攝時弗蘭西斯就在旁邊\NFrancis was there during the shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是一份生日禮物\NIt was a birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾問我想要什麼樣的肖像\NClaire asked me what sort of portrait I wanted,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說就拍她睡覺的樣子吧\Nand I said I want one of her sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為她睡著的時候非常美\Nbecause she's so very beautiful when she's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片就掛在我二樓的辦公室裏\NIt hangs in my office on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在說謊\NThey're fucking lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.27,0:14:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只能猜測\NSo I can only assume
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當被媒體的關注嚇到了\Nthat Adam was intimidated by the media attention,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想撇清關係\Nand he needed to distance himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.96,0:14:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但真相其實就是\NBut really, all we have here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.62,0:14:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一位才華橫溢的攝影師\Nis a very talented photographer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而這是一幅我們很喜愛的作品\Nand a prized possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝你們\NThank you all very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.74,0:14:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為那樣看上去就太清白了  好像我們...\NBecause it would've seemed too clean otherwise, like we were--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我丟盡了臉\NYou made me look like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們說法一致\NIf we had the same story,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媒體會認為我們是串通好了\Nthe media would assume we were coordinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必須亂一些\NIt needed to look messier.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這事本該結束的  克萊爾\NThis was supposed to go away, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.46,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在我樓外的記者多了一倍\NI've got twice as much press outside the building now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當\NAdam...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不把燈都關上\NI've gotta keep the lights off
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.56,0:15:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們在對面樓頂上  想要拍我們\N'cause they're on the roof across the street, trying to film us inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只需要證實照片是你為我們拍攝的\NYou just need to confirm that you took the photo for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證實我們的說法\NConfirm our version.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說你說謊是因為你害怕了\NSay you lied because you were scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白你為什麼不事先\NI don't know why you didn't just tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你要做的告訴我\Nthis is what you were intending to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我瞭解你  你會拒絕的\NBecause I know you, and you would've refused.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自尊心太強了\NYou have too much pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再面對媒體了\NI don't want to speak to the press again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.20,0:15:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著\NListen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你什麼都不說\NIf you say nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會放過你的\Nthey're not going to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們會在外面守上幾星期\NThey will just camp out for weeks on end--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...我覺得這樣不對  克萊爾\NThis is... it feels wrong, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得...\NIt feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉我說謊了\NI'm sorry I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是想擺佈你\NI wasn't trying to be manipulative--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.07,0:15:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要掛了\NI have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.57,0:15:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當\NAdam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當\NAdam?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.62,0:15:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他會想通的\NI think he'll do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  但願吧\NI don't know. I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.72,0:15:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要來支煙嗎\NCigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我去睡了\NNo. I'm gonna turn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他上電視了叫我\NWake me if he goes on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.51,0:16:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-先生  -道格\N- Sir. - Doug,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和賽斯過來一下\Nwhy don't you and Seth come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要考慮起訴這家報紙\NShould we consider a lawsuit against the paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表明我們不容忍這種八卦\NShow we won't tolerate this sort of gossip?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會和解的\NThey won't settle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們樂意上法庭  這樣能製造更多新聞\NThey'll fight it in the courts because it'll generate more news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統那兒呢\NAnd what about the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他提出要表個態\NHe offered to say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣熱度就更高了\NDraws more attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總統發話不是個壞主意\NPresident isn't a bad idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們幫他起草講話稿\Nif we phrase a statement for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他成了頭條新聞\NHe becomes the headline
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們控制不了他的媒體策略\Nand we can't control his press operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們和他們協調好  就不會...\NBut if we coordinate with them, it shouldn't --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,協調會讓人生疑\NCoordination looks bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得讓人看不出痕跡啊\NSo it's your job to conceal it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.76,0:16:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果賽斯覺得總統的講話有弊無利\NIf Seth doesn't think the president should make a comment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.88,0:16:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們就相信他的判斷吧\Nthen we should defer to his judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.07,0:16:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再去拿瓶啤酒\NI'm gonna go get another beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我幫你去拿吧  -不用  我正想活動下手腳\N- I can go grab you one, sir. - No. I feel like stretching my legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  來罐健怡可樂\NDoug, diet Coke?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  謝謝  先生\NI'm fine, thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯  來瓶啤酒\NSeth, a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還得開車  謝了\NI have to drive, but thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.59,0:16:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去去就回\NI'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你給我小心點\NWatch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康納很容易扳倒\NConnor was an easy target,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.52,0:17:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我可不是\Nbut I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格  能有這位置我已經很滿意了\NLook, doug, I'm grateful just to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在副總統身邊這麼久\NYou think I've survived with the vice president
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這點小花招還看不出來\Nso long by being blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給他們工作的晉陞空間是有上限的\NUpward mobility has a ceiling with the Underwoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是上限\NI'm the ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了\NUnderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你手裏還有他們什麼把柄\NWhat else have you got on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.13,0:17:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你交出日記的時候沒留一手嗎\NYou fork over the journal without a backup plan for a rainy day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.03,0:17:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有什麼牌就出什麼牌\NI had one hand and I played it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會冒險\NI don't press my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會指望我會相信吧\NYou can't expect me to believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒指望\NI don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換做我是你我也不相信\NI wouldn't if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我說的是實話\NBut I'm telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兄弟間的小鬥爭不是什麼壞事\NA little sibling rivalry isn't such a bad thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在養子之間\Nespecially between adopted boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要麼彼此施壓\NThey either push each other
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都更上一層樓\Nto be the best versions of themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要麼其中一人被踢回孤兒院\Nor one of them gets booted back to the orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我家  我喝你們也得喝\NYou're in my house. You drink if I drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的健怡可樂  你的啤酒\NOne Diet Coke for you, and one beer for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  先生\NThank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的  真是一團糟\NOh, darling, what a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的\NSweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們還撐得住嗎\NHow are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媒體接連騷擾了我們兩天\NThe press have been harassing us the past two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們好不容易離開公寓  差點被他們踩死\Nwe barely made it out of the building without being trampled.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了\NOh, how awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說這兒有人要見我\NYou said someone was here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在我辦公室\NHe's in my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告訴你他是誰了嗎\NDid he tell you who he was?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想在電話裏說\NI didn't want to say over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這世道什麼都說不准\NYou never know, these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他以前為安德伍德夫婦工作\NHe says he used to work for the Underwoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.69,0:18:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是誰  -你的助理\N- Who? - Your assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.62,0:18:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不  她不會...  -她會  她做了\N- No, she would never-- - She would and she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼目的\NWhy are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不是我  是我的老闆  -那是誰\N- Not me. The man I work for. - And who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這與你無關\NThat doesn't concern you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是在攪和我的生活\NThis is my life you're fucking with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我都只是小卒  嘉樂威先生\NYou and I are just pawns, Mr. Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走吧\NYou should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要更多證據...\NWe need more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.84,0:18:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證明這事發生過  再給我一張照片\N...to prove the affair happened. Another photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給你30秒  走出這扇門\NThirty seconds, you better be out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哪也不去\NI'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,認識這個國家區號嗎\NYou recognize the country code?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城市區號是波哥大的\NAnd the city code is Bogota.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒人接聽嗎\NIs it still ringing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬歇爾\NMarshall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爹\NHey, pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天  從沒見這裏這麼火\NMan, never seen it like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊都排到街上了\NThe line's down the block.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺壯觀  是吧\NSomething else, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你需要人幫忙\NLooks like you could use some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後廚還有條圍裙\NGot a extra apron in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹活兒了\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她賴在門廳不肯走\NShe refuses to leave the lobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什麼\NWhat's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾拉·薩伊德  《華爾街電訊報》的\NAyla Sayyad, Wall Street Telegraph.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.62,0:19:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是副總統記者團的成員\NShe's part of the Vice President's press corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫她上來吧\NSend her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你了  特莉莎  我沒事\NI appreciate it, tricia, but I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事鬧個一兩天也就過去了\NThis whole thing will blow over in a day or so,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時我再\Nand I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能稍等下嗎\NCan you hold on one second?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.86,0:20:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《日報》來電  他們要你發表評論\NThe Daily. They called for a comment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞當和他們談過了嗎\NDid Adam speak with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,談過了  但不是按我們的要求說的\NYes, but not what we told him to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.63,0:20:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他把這個發給報社了\NHe sent them this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特莉莎  我能過會兒再打給你嗎\NTricia, can I call you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-這是你嗎  -不是\N- Is that you? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.86,0:20:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他說這就是你\NBecause he's saying it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-可能是  -安德伍德夫人\N- It might be. - Mrs. Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能是  沒錯\NI mean, it could be, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是\NIt probably is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我特地問過你還有沒有別的把柄\NI asked you about any vulnerabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他拍了這張\NI didn't know he took this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.85,0:20:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片裏你留著短髮\NYou have short hair in the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說過戀情兩年前就斷了\NYou said it ended over two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去年秋天去過他那兒\NWell, I visited him last fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有別人知道嗎  有誰在那兒見到過你嗎\NDoes anyone else know? Did anyone see you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他請朋友去過他的公寓\NHe had friends over, to his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天\NChrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.31,0:21:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們說過他是位朋友了\NBut we've said that he's a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拜訪他  參加聚會沒什麼問題\NThere's nothing wrong with me visiting him, being at a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等這照片上了《日報》的頭版就有問題了\NThere is if this photo is on the front page of the Daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.01,0:21:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在中國  政治和生意是糾纏不清的\NPolitics and business are intertwined in China,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.85,0:21:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想必你知道這一點\Nas I'm sure you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.28,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了確保中央政府的許可\NIt's not uncommon to partner
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結交有門路的合作夥伴很正常\Nwith someone who can ensure Beijing's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說你需要他的政治影響力\NSo you needed his political influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,費盡心機  我們的合作還是泡湯了\NAll this is moot. Our venture fell through.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在傑斐遜港大橋獲批之後\NRight after the Port Jefferson Bridge was approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和那項工程沒有任何關係\NI had nothing to do with that project.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知  馮也沒有\NNeither did Feng, to my knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒有  但是吳彬陽投了資\NNo, but Wu Bin Yang did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.36,0:21:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是馮在北京的主要競爭對手\NHe's Feng's biggest rival in Beijing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.54,0:21:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我沒資格給你上中國政治課了\NIt looks like I shouldn't be schooling you on Chinese politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.63,0:21:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你比我瞭解的多啊\NYou know far more than I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你用了"糾纏不清"這個詞\NYou used the word "Intertwined."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這正是我對整件事的感受\NThat's the sense I'm getting from all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,核能補貼  中國精煉廠  大橋工程\NThe samarium subsidy, the Chinese refinery, the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及你和總統的關係\Nyour friendship with the President...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.12,0:21:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰派你來的\NWho sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.81,0:22:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼派我來\NWho sent me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,財富積累到我這種程度\NWhen you're as rich as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.59,0:22:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就總得提防明槍暗箭\Nyou're always a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己找來的\NNobody sent me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你坐在這兒\NYou're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在聖路易斯採訪\Nin St. Louis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.61,0:22:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是去報道副總統夫婦的醜聞\NInstead of covering the vice president and his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得馮山德背後還有更多隱情\NMy gut says there's more to Xander Feng than has been reported.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.85,0:22:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-是嗎  -把時間花在這上面\N- Yeah. - It's a far better use of my time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比報道什麼八卦性醜聞更值得\Nthan reporting on tabloid sex scandals.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.90,0:22:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是真正的新聞\NIt's not real news.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懷念德黑蘭了吧\NYou miss Tehran.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在下面等待時  我讀了幾篇你的文章\NI read some of your work while you were in the waiting area.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.93,0:22:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-那裏越來越危險了  -可不是\N- It started to get too dangerous. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那種環境不適合\NNot the best place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結婚成家  生兒育女\Nwhen you want to get married and start a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者猶太人\NOr if you're Jewish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對\NThat, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.24,0:22:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太太去那兒旅遊時給我買了這個回來\NMy wife got this for me when she visited there,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.95,0:22:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是在伊斯蘭革命之前\Nbefore the revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮\NIt's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.53,0:22:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,16世紀的古董\N16th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.45,0:22:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,托運回國的時候被弄碎了\NIt, um, broke when it was being shipped,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.16,0:22:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摔得粉碎\Ninto a thousand pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好幾名專家花了一年多才修復如初\NIt took specialists over a year to restore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給  我希望你能收下\NHere, I want you to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能接受你的禮物\NI can't accept gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.52,0:23:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不  這不是禮物\NNo, no. Not as a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是給你提個醒\NNo. As a reminder of how hard it can be to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些東西一旦碎了  再拼起來就難了\Nput something back together again once it's been crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.91,0:23:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要是想威脅我的話\NIf you're going to threaten me,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不用這麼兜圈子\Nyou don't have to go to the trouble of veiling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一般不接受記者採訪\NI don't usually do interviews with reporters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就是寄生蟲\NThey're parasites.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:34.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大都一心琢磨怎麼想辦法打擊我\NUsually interested in just finding a way to knock me down a peg.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自然而然\NInvariably,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們寫的東西都不準確\Nwhat they write is inaccurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.65,0:23:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們不如實寫\NAnd when that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不得不反擊了\NI have no choice but to retaliate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.85,0:23:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美國也可以像伊朗一樣危險  薩伊德小姐\NAmerica can be just as dangerous as Iran, ms. Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.79,0:24:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你抽時間見我  塔斯克先生\NThank you for your time, mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.64,0:24:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回華盛頓的路上注意安全\NTravel safe back to Washington.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.25,0:24:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給雷米打電話\NGet Remy on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.20,0:24:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米在二線\NRemy's on line two.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.09,0:24:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷米\NRemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.11,0:24:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不要再留後手了\NLet's not hold back on the other thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.17,0:24:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次打擊他  現在就執行\NHit 'em again, and hit 'em now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收益最好的一天\NBest day yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.42,0:24:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得弄個保險箱什麼的\NYou gotta get a safe or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.66,0:24:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者讓銀行上門收存款什麼的\NOr maybe one of those, uh, pickup services.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.35,0:24:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上帶這麼多錢走路太危險了\NThat's too much money to be carrying around at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.25,0:24:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能應付\NI can handle myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對著槍口還怎麼應付\NThere ain't nobody can handle a Glock to the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.61,0:24:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你自己有一把\NUnless you got one yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.16,0:24:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就不帶傢伙了\NMy days of packin' are long gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.34,0:24:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來\NThere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.04,0:24:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿我的\NTake mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.60,0:24:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家裏還有一把\NI got one at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.06,0:25:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把那東西帶到這裏來幹什麼\NWhat the fuck you doin' bringin' that thing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.75,0:25:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是為了安全\NOh, it's just for protection, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.69,0:25:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不知道你為什麼要有槍\NI don't know what you doing with it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.81,0:25:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的假釋條例怎麼辦\NWhat about your parole?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.09,0:25:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起假釋官我更擔心\NI'm a lot more worried about niggas in my building
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.92,0:25:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家樓裏的黑鬼們\Nthan some parole officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.77,0:25:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  坐下\NAll right, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.66,0:25:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你瞧  我說的就是這個\NSee, man? This is what I'm talkin' about, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.15,0:25:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自以為是地評價我\NYou being all righteous and judgin' me and shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.92,0:25:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我個面子  坐下  快點\NDo me a favor and just sit down. Sit down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著\NLook.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.27,0:25:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們可能遇到件好事\NWe got us a good thing, potentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.06,0:25:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能最終沒有結果  也可能會有好結果\NMaybe nothing comes of it, but maybe something does.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.17,0:25:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果連鎖店成功\NIf the joint works out,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.89,0:25:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有一天你能當經理\Nmaybe one day you could be the manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.63,0:25:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真的火起來\NShit, if it blows up,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.90,0:25:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能去經營整個連鎖店\Nyou could run the whole fucking franchise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.19,0:25:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那意味著你得小心點\NBut that means you gotta be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.18,0:25:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能再被抓回去了\NThat means you cannot be sent back inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.63,0:25:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們得遵紀守法\NWe gotta follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.09,0:25:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了嗎\NHear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.90,0:26:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.68,0:26:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你會處理掉那東西嗎\NYou gonna get rid of that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.69,0:26:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.54,0:26:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.63,0:26:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這才像個男人\NNow that's what's being a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.85,0:26:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你剪短頭髮\NI'll need you to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.69,0:26:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多短\NHow short?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.27,0:26:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼短\NThis short.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.59,0:26:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還要做模特呢  如果我剪那麼短\NI have a modeling career. If I cut it that short--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.84,0:26:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真有模特工作\NIf you actually had a modeling career,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.77,0:26:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就會在和你經紀人談\NI would be speaking to your agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.39,0:26:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是坐在你的公寓裏\Nand not sitting in your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.60,0:26:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想不想要這份工作\NDo you want this job or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NOK, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.85,0:26:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以剪短\NI can cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.02,0:26:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.98,0:26:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我們去攝影棚之前\NAnd before we go to the studio,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.54,0:26:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要知道你是否口齒清楚\NI need to see how well-spoken you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.50,0:26:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這有什麼關係\NWhy does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.55,0:26:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你會出現在全美所有的新聞頻道上\NBecause you're gonna be on every news channel in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.73,0:26:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  這是怎麼回事\NWait. What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.47,0:27:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀出這個  一字不差\NRead this. Those exact words.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.53,0:27:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀出來\NRead 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.47,0:27:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有本事  就該背出來\NIf you're good, you'll memorize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.88,0:27:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是斯特芬妮·道瑞\NMy name is Stephanie Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.36,0:27:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名職業模特\NI am a professional model.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.66,0:27:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪·海耶斯因在哥倫比亞高地\NFreddy Hayes was convicted in 1982
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.01,0:27:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搶劫一家便利店  而於1982年被定罪\Nfor sticking up a convenience store in Columbia Heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.46,0:27:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在高速追捕中\NDuring a high-speed pursuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.78,0:27:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海耶斯失控撞向另一輛車\NHayes lost control and crashed into another vehicle,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.79,0:27:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,導致一對老夫婦死亡\Nkilling an elderly couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.96,0:27:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他承認犯有持械搶劫罪\NHe avoided manslaughter charges
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.43,0:27:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以免受過失殺人的起訴\Nby pleading guilty to armed robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.81,0:27:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他服刑九年\NHe served nine years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.24,0:27:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1992年他開了弗萊迪燒烤餐館\NIn 1992 he opened Freddy's BBQ Joint,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.15,0:27:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一家專做肋排的小餐館\Na small restaurant specializing in ribs,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.21,0:27:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副總統弗蘭克·安德伍德是那裏的常客\Nfrequented by Vice President Frank Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎\NDid you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.26,0:27:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不知道\NNo, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.07,0:27:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為是塔斯克\NYou think it's Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.15,0:27:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能是誰\NWho else?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.35,0:28:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在給誰發短信\NWho are you texting?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.32,0:28:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽斯\NSeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.64,0:28:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想發佈一份簡短聲明\NAll I want to do is make a short statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.01,0:28:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪已經服過刑了\NFreddy did his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.62,0:28:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他20年來一直遵紀守法\NHe's been an upstanding citizen for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.80,0:28:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是個殺死兩位老人的罪犯\NHe's a convicted felon who killed two senior citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.43,0:28:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是意外\NBy accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.58,0:28:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是重點\NWell, that's beside the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.48,0:28:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能不管他\NI am not gonna hang him out to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.37,0:28:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有嘉樂威的事\NIf the Galloway story wasn't happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.06,0:28:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這可以\NI'd say it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.42,0:28:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但現在太冒險了\NBut it's too risky right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.40,0:28:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想這看起來像什麼樣\NThink of how this is shaping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.99,0:28:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個戴綠帽子\NA vice president whose wife cheats on him
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.74,0:28:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還和前罪犯做朋友的副總統\Nand who is friendly with a former gang-banger?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.82,0:28:38.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你維護他不會有好結果\NThere is no way you win standing up for this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.02,0:28:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他馬上要開連鎖店了\NHe's about to start a franchise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.58,0:28:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不容許這事告吹\NI will not have it jeopardized
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.86,0:28:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就因為塔斯克決定針對...\Nbecause Tusk decides to come after --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.54,0:28:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不單是弗萊迪的問題  先生\NIs more than just Freddy, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.00,0:28:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做過調查\NI did some digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.53,0:28:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他兒子因運毒和販毒坐過牢\NHis son did time for narcotics, trafficking, distribution--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.34,0:28:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒見過他兒子\NI've never met his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.58,0:28:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事再緩緩  先解決\NLet's hold off and tackle--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.93,0:28:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  明早安排我跟記者見一下面\NNo. I want you to organize a press avail tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.44,0:28:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派人接弗萊迪過來\NHave Freddy brought over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.40,0:28:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從後門進\NBring him through the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.14,0:28:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.97,0:29:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會對自己人見死不救\NI won't leave one of my own bleeding on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.85,0:29:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是華盛頓紅人隊\NIf you're gonna have the Washington Redskins,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.77,0:29:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那對手必須是紐約尼克斯隊\Nthen you're gonna have to have the New York Knickers.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.77,0:29:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}華盛頓紅人是美式足球隊  紐約尼克斯是籃球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.46,0:29:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸  你完全弄錯了\NPops, you ain't even deep like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.72,0:29:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走開  夥計\NYo, back off, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.32,0:29:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都他媽滾開\NBack the fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.38,0:29:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾  別理他們就好\NDarnell, just ignore them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.25,0:29:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當我在開玩笑嗎\NYou think I'm fucking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.36,0:29:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾  別理他們\NDarnell, ignore them! Ignore 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.15,0:29:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想被拍  他們就不能拍\NThey can't take our pictures if we don't want them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.21,0:29:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老子當然能\NSure as hell can.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.66,0:29:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\NWhat you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.56,0:29:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}美國憲法第一修正案保護新聞自由
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.56,0:29:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一修正案\NThe First fuckin' Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.48,0:29:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他媽要給我講憲法嗎\NYou gonna read me the constitution now, motherfucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.59,0:29:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了  達奈爾  我們進去吧\NCome on, Darnell. Let's just go on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.48,0:29:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我和這混蛋還沒完\NNah, nah, I ain't done with this asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.72,0:29:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我\NHey, don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.04,0:29:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能威脅我\NBut you can get all up in my face
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.36,0:29:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻不能威脅你嗎\Nbut I can't get up in yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.52,0:29:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-聽你爸的  冷靜點  -達奈爾  我們走吧\N- Listen to your daddy and chill out. - Darnell, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.02,0:29:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別逼我\NDon't push me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.99,0:29:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心我揍你\NI will fuck you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.25,0:29:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我怕你嗎\NYou think I'm scared of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.39,0:29:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怕這個嗎\NYou scared of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.40,0:29:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾  你的保釋\NDarnell! Parole!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.29,0:29:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能告訴我你的名字嗎\NCan you tell me your name, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.89,0:29:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斯特芬妮·道瑞\NStephanie Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.20,0:29:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是一名職業模特\NI'm a professional model.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.02,0:30:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右邊照片裏的人是你嗎\NAnd this is you in this photo on the right?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.93,0:30:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\NYes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.13,0:30:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道瑞小姐的這張照是昨天拍的\NWe shot this photo yesterday with Ms. Daldry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.86,0:30:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說嘉樂威先生的照片是假的嗎\NSo you're suggesting that Mr. Galloway's photo is a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.37,0:30:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對專業攝影一無所知\NI don't know anything about professional photography,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.75,0:30:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個做宣傳的\NI'm just a flack.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.71,0:30:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我們都能在24小時內偽造照片\NBut if we can create a fake in less than 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.23,0:30:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像亞當·嘉樂威那樣的專業攝影師...\NI think an expert photographer like Adam Galloway--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.29,0:30:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這指控相當嚴重\NThose are serious allegations,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.65,0:30:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在嘉樂威先生極力否認的情況下\Nespecially given that Mr. Galloway vehemently denies it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.22,0:30:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對他的否認並不意外\NI'm not surprised he's denying.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.12,0:30:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過最後就是你們兩人對質了\NUltimately, though, it's gonna be your word against his.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.67,0:30:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我\NNot my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.27,0:30:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是美國的副總統\NThe vice president of the United States'.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.73,0:30:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他和一個可能有問題的人的對質\NIt's his word versus that of a potentially troubled man.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.45,0:30:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題\NTroubled?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.44,0:30:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能\NPotentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.32,0:30:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許他是有動機的\NOr maybe he has a motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.24,0:30:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉樂威先生會有什麼造假的動機呢\NWhat motive could Mr. Galloway possibly have for a fake photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.35,0:30:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能從中得到什麼\NWhat would he get out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.82,0:30:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.39,0:30:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作是區分事實和虛構\NMy job is to separate fact from fiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.54,0:30:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點和你一樣  坎迪\Njust like yours is, Candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.53,0:30:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但或許對搞藝術的人來說\NBut maybe fact and fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.42,0:30:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事實和虛構不那麼重要\Ndon't matter as much to the artistic sensibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.86,0:30:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許他分得不那麼清楚\NMaybe the lines are blurred for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.57,0:30:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他並不拍攝虛構的作品\NThis is not a man who stages fictitious scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.16,0:30:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也說了  我不懂藝術\NLike I said, the art stuff, it's over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.99,0:31:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許你是對的\NAnd you may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.00,0:31:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不願相信\NBut I would hate to think
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.17,0:31:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉樂威先生這麼做僅僅是為了炒作\Nthat Mr. Galloway was doing this just for publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.25,0:31:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為這是炒作\NYou think it's a publicity stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.69,0:31:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來\NCome on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.22,0:31:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生\NSir?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.86,0:31:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪在路上了嗎\NIs Freddy on his way?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.48,0:31:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他兒子出事了\NThere was an incident with his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.95,0:31:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼\NWhat happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.87,0:31:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他因持槍威脅攝像師被警方拘留\NHe's in custody for threatening a photographer with a firearm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.06,0:31:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.36,0:31:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪現在在哪\NWhere is Freddy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.51,0:31:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在家\NHe's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.76,0:31:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得去看他\NI have to go see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.29,0:31:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是貧困住宅區\NThat's the projects, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.16,0:31:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管  你看著辦\NI don't care, you figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.62,0:31:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且不能讓媒體知道\Nand the press can't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.60,0:31:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.82,0:31:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯  我也很喜歡弗萊迪\NFrancis, you know I love Freddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.80,0:31:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要去\NI'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.79,0:31:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗萊迪有危險  是因為你太在乎他\NFreddy is dangerous because you care too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.16,0:31:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過在乎  會使人盲目\NWhen we care too much, it blinds us.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.95,0:31:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔斯克的做法太卑鄙了\NWhat Tusk did is cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.93,0:31:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻讓這事影響到你  這正是他的目的\NAnd you're letting it get to you, which is exactly what he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.46,0:31:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我視而不見  無所作為\NIf I ignore this, if I do nothing--
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.69,0:31:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是無所作為\NIt's not nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.49,0:31:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持專注也需要力量\NStaying focused requires strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.77,0:32:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我給你做點什麼嗎\NYou want me to make something?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.66,0:32:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃吧  我不餓\NYou go ahead. I'm not hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.62,0:32:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得吃點\NYou should eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.61,0:32:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  這本來跟你無關\NI'm sorry. You didn't ask for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.64,0:32:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對你不公平\NIt's not fair to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.54,0:32:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想快點結束\NAll I want is to be done with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.83,0:32:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我父親平安\NFor my father to be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.26,0:32:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我當時還有別的辦法...\NIf I thought there was any other way, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.14,0:32:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想冒險讓他...\NI didn't want to take the chance that he would--
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.68,0:32:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.75,0:32:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些人\NThese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.37,0:32:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一向知道他們很無情  但是\NI always knew they were ruthless, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.67,0:32:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們像動物一樣關在這裏\NWe're caged up in here like animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.65,0:32:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們把我刻畫成了那種...\NThey're painting me as some sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.34,0:32:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有你的家人\NAnd your family...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.96,0:32:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太殘忍了\NIt's inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.70,0:32:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們太他媽殘忍了\NThey're fucking inhuman.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.32,0:32:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生氣也不能改變局面\NGetting worked up isn't going to change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.53,0:32:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來\NLet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.02,0:32:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.76,0:33:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭克\NHey, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.64,0:33:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了\NI'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.50,0:33:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你來看我\NThanks for dropping by.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.41,0:33:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎\NHow you holdin' up?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.76,0:33:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湊合吧\NI been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.39,0:33:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從沒見過你不穿西裝的樣子\NAin't never seen you without a suit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.02,0:33:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不想太招人注意\NWe didn't want to draw too much attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.83,0:33:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  我的城堡\NWell, this is it, my castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.86,0:33:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如你的大  但也夠用了\NAin't as big as yours, but it'll do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.48,0:33:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盲眼威利Blind Willie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.48,0:33:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}盲眼威利·約翰遜  美國福音藍調歌手  吉他演奏家
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.43,0:33:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡藍調嗎\NAre you a blues fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.08,0:33:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《漆黑的夜晚》  每次聽都讓我陶醉\N"Dark Was the Night." Gets me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.80,0:33:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夥計  你早該告訴我\NMan, you shoulda told me that years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.71,0:33:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會即興演奏  聊起藍調能聊一整天\NI can jam, talking about some blues all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.45,0:34:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這張  78年原版\NCheck this out. Original 78.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.49,0:34:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要喝點什麼嗎\NYou want something?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.52,0:34:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水  還是冰茶\NWater? Iced tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.01,0:34:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要冰茶  謝謝\NI'd like some iced tea, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.60,0:34:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你兒子怎麼樣了\NHow's your son?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.01,0:34:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要六萬保釋金\NThey set the bail at 60 grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.66,0:34:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天哪\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.90,0:34:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子怎麼樣了\NHow's your wife doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.56,0:34:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克萊爾有一副三英吋厚的鎧甲\NOh, Claire's got a suit of armor three inches thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.47,0:34:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些難關我們會撐過去的\NWe'll get through all this garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.20,0:34:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人想毀了你嗎\NSomebody's tryin' to take you out?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.93,0:34:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是的\NAppears that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.79,0:34:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰\NWhoever it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.69,0:34:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們踩到不該踩的響尾蛇了\Nthey done stepped on the wrong motherfuckin' rattlesnake.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.84,0:34:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我來這裏了  弗萊迪\NThat's why I'm here, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.82,0:34:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得遠離你\NI have to distance myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.84,0:34:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要確保你不會到處宣揚\NI need to make sure you're not going to play up
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.92,0:34:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是多好的朋友\Nwhat good friends we've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.94,0:34:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說你去過我的辦公室\NThat you've been to my office,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.73,0:34:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還曾在我家做晚餐\Nthat you've cooked dinner at my home,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.92,0:35:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且總統也出席了那次晚餐\Nor that the president was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.97,0:35:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能連累了他\NWe can't drag him into anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.30,0:35:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不會來吃肋排了\NAnd I won't be coming in for ribs anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.06,0:35:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在出了這麼多事\NWith all that's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.16,0:35:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不能再火上澆油了\Nwe can't add fuel to the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.20,0:35:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是想來吃也吃不到了\NYou couldn't if you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.95,0:35:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要賣掉了\NI'm selling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.38,0:35:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賣掉餐館嗎\NSelling the Joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.60,0:35:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.41,0:35:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呢\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.45,0:35:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醬汁的特許經營權什麼的\NThe franchise thing, with the sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.64,0:35:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生意夥伴要解約了\NMy business partner's pullin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.05,0:35:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說他們銀泉的白人不喜歡去\NSay them white folks down in Silver Spring don't wanna
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.67,0:35:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惡棍開的餐館\Ngo to no place run by thugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.02,0:35:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼非得賣掉你的店\NWhy do you have to sell yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.69,0:35:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,達奈爾的保釋金\NDarnell's bail.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.14,0:35:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙不是無論如何都得給你十萬美金嗎\NDoesn't that guy have to give you a hundred grand, regardless?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.92,0:35:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我屁都拿不到\NI ain't getting shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.46,0:35:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合同里有一條道德條款\NThere's a morality clause in the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.60,0:35:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他打算花四萬五買我的門面\NBut he's gonna pay me 45 thou for the storefront.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.47,0:35:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上我存的一點錢  就可以付保釋金了\NThat with what little I got saved, I can pay that bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.24,0:35:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能把餐館賣掉\NYou can't sell Freddy's.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.72,0:36:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已經在起草合同了\NHe's already drawing up the papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.56,0:36:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫你解決錢的問題\NLet me help you with the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.03,0:36:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  弗蘭克\NNah, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.64,0:36:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就當做是借貸\NWe'll make it a loan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.44,0:36:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以以後再還我\NYou can pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.39,0:36:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行\NNot gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.11,0:36:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別要強\NDon't be prideful.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.92,0:36:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-弗蘭克  -拜託  讓我幫你吧\N- Frank. - Please, let me help.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.34,0:36:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是內疚  我不會要的\NI ain't takin' your guilt money.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.54,0:36:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去在道上的時候\NWhen I was bangin',
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.38,0:36:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一個月能賺六萬美金\Nwe used to clear 60 Gs a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.13,0:36:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我見過同伴被人殘忍槍殺\NI seen guys shot down execution-style.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.73,0:36:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我一點也不關心\NI didn't give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.78,0:36:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後我被捕了\NThen I got caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.82,0:36:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐牢的第一年裏達奈爾出生了\NDarnell was born my first year in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.44,0:36:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一次也沒見過他  連照片都沒有\NNever saw him once, not even a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.88,0:36:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能收回我所犯的罪惡\NI can't take back the bad I done.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.09,0:36:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所能做的就是一如既往\NAll I can do is to make my own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.42,0:36:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己想辦法活下去  你明白嗎\Nlike I've been doing. You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.81,0:36:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要強  弗蘭克\NAin't pride, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.89,0:37:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你改變心意了  就告訴我\NIf you change your mind, you let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.30,0:37:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是一個好顧客  僅此而已\NYou was a good customer, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.81,0:37:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必假裝是我的朋友\NYou ain't gotta pretend to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.86,0:37:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多保重  弗萊迪\NYou take care of yourself, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.80,0:37:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是  弗蘭克\NYou too, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.23,0:37:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我是一個偽君子嗎\NDo you think I'm a hypocrite?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.75,0:37:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就對了\NWell, you should.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.65,0:37:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會否認\NI wouldn't disagree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.28,0:37:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通向權利的道路由虛偽\NThe road to power is paved with hypocrisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.68,0:37:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和犧牲鋪就\N...and casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.60,0:37:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不要後悔\NNever regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.86,0:38:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請\NThis way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.07,0:38:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請坐  亞當\NHave a seat, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.45,0:38:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你按要求的那樣  把電話留在家裏了嗎\NYou left your phone at home, as you were asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.22,0:38:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.78,0:38:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼跟你未婚妻說的\NAnd what did you tell your fiancee exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.23,0:38:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就說我要離開一陣子\NThat I'd be gone for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.68,0:38:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不知道我要去哪\NShe doesn't know where.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.94,0:38:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人找到她  她會說什麼\NAnd what will she say if someone checks in on her?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.84,0:38:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是幹什麼\NWhat is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.53,0:38:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她會說什麼\NWhat will she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.55,0:38:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗蘭西斯\NFrancis.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.79,0:39:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在得協調合作\NWe need to work together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.40,0:39:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我試過  但你騙了我\NI tried. You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.18,0:39:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我也解釋了為什麼要那麼做\NAnd I explained to you why that was necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.49,0:39:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可你不聽我的命令\NYou didn't follow my instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.04,0:39:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們知道雷米·丹頓是誰嗎\NDo you know who Remy Danton is?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.56,0:39:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他找過你嗎\NHe approached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.13,0:39:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊奈茲的父親是波哥大的一位人權運動家\NInez's father is a human rights activist in Bogota.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.94,0:39:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府說他勾結叛亂分子\NThe government has charged him with treason
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.33,0:39:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,控告他叛國\Nfor working with the rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.18,0:39:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們要判他死刑\NThey're going for the death penalty,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.40,0:39:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹頓說他們可以操縱法官\Nand Danton said they have the judge in their pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.66,0:39:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你應該來找我們\NYou should have come to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.47,0:39:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟他說了\NI said I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.34,0:39:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丹頓說你什麼也做不了\NDanton said you couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.63,0:39:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他錯了\NHe's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.82,0:39:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能冒險\NI wasn't gonna take any chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.21,0:39:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她父親如政府所稱那樣犯罪了嗎\NHas he done what the government's claiming?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.41,0:39:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有  都是些無中生有的指控\NNo. They're made-up charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.76,0:39:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是一個記者\NHe's a journalist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.46,0:39:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報道達恩地塹那裏的殘暴行徑\Ndocumenting atrocities in the Darien Gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.46,0:39:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}巴拿馬與哥倫比亞之間未開發的大片沼澤地
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.51,0:39:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以撤銷指控\NI can get the charges dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.92,0:39:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我憑什麼相信你\NWhy should I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.82,0:39:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為國務卿是我的好朋友\NBecause the secretary of state is a good friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.07,0:39:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你別無選擇\NAnd you don't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.81,0:39:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是你的棋子\NWe're not your chess pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.69,0:39:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也不是遊戲  嘉樂威先生\NAnd this isn't a game, Mr. Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.60,0:39:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你為什麼要耍我們\NThen why are you toying with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.71,0:39:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是想幫你\NWe are trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.59,0:40:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑  克萊爾\NThat's a fucking joke, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.91,0:40:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不准這樣和我妻子說話\NDo not talk to my wife that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.37,0:40:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妻子  那對你來說有什麼意義\NYour wife. What does that even mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.51,0:40:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別因為你們之間有過一段歷史\NDo not mistake any history you have shared
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.18,0:40:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就以為你瞭解我們的婚姻\Nfor the slightest understanding of what our marriage is
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.00,0:40:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相比之下  你完全無關緊要\Nor how insignificant you are in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.14,0:40:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我倆單獨談談嗎\NCan you give us a few minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.38,0:40:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去給凱茜打電話\NI'm gonna go call Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.15,0:40:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不說我的事業和名聲吧\NForget my career and my reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.60,0:40:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和這個女人結婚  克萊爾\NI want to marry this woman, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.90,0:40:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會擺平這件事的\NWe're going to make this disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.79,0:40:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你  我將永遠是那個\NBecause of you I will always be the man
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.48,0:40:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將她父親置於險境的人\Nwho placed her father in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.05,0:40:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這永遠無法抹去\NI can never erase that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.28,0:40:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾事情走到了這個地步\NI'm sorry it's come to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.76,0:40:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真後悔遇見你\NI'm sorry I ever met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.95,0:40:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從頭到尾  你只給過我痛苦\NAll you've ever done is cause me pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.18,0:40:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你又來破壞我的生活\NNow you're fucking with my life
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.23,0:40:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有我未婚妻的生活\Nand the life of the woman
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.24,0:40:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛她遠勝過愛你\Nthat I love more than I ever loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.66,0:40:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你今晚就開車回紐約\NYou'll be driven back to New York tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.78,0:40:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天一早  你就發表聲明\NIn the morning, you'll make a statement saying
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.40,0:41:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說這是炒作\Nthis was a publicity stunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.53,0:41:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的作品一直賣不出好價錢\Nand that the value of your work had been stagnating
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.51,0:41:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-所以你希望重振...  -不  克萊爾\N- and you wanted to revive - No, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.76,0:41:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我才不會那樣做  -你會的\N- I won't do that. - Yes, you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.61,0:41:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如我去告訴記者\NHow about I tell the press,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.64,0:41:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我被帶到這兒來  -亞當  閉嘴\N- that you, that I was brought here - Adam, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.33,0:41:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要說你想博取關注  然後又害怕了\NThat you wanted the attention, then you got cold feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.22,0:41:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否認了照片的事  接著又再次改了主意\Ndenied it, then you changed your mind again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.73,0:41:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張浴室照片是你偽造的\NAnd that you faked the shower photo
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.71,0:41:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要澄清這一點\Nand you're coming clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.13,0:41:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎\NIs that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.30,0:41:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該被捲進這種事中\NI'm not part of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.74,0:41:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想攪進來  我也不感興趣\NI didn't sign up for it. I have no interest in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.62,0:41:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們給你提供了一條出路  亞當\NWe're giving you an out, Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.08,0:41:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你選擇不接受的話\NAnd if you choose not to take it,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.66,0:41:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會毀掉你\NI will bury you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.03,0:41:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒恨過任何人\NI've never hated anyone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.19,0:41:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我知道那是什麼感覺了\NNow I know what that feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.48,0:41:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很糟  對嗎\NIt's a terrible feeling, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.11,0:42:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終止呼叫\NEnd call.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.44,0:42:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫已終止\NCall ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.63,0:42:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫雷蒙德·塔斯克\NCall Raymond Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.61,0:42:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的住處沒人接電話\NNo answer at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.89,0:42:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是想要更多錢嗎\NIs it a matter of more money?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.81,0:42:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國務卿杜蘭特已經致電莫裏諾總統\NSecretary Durant has already called President Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.37,0:42:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們得趕快行動了\NSo we need to move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.16,0:42:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外交部長已經牽扯進來了\NThe minister of foreign affairs is involved now.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.47,0:42:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官不會在12小時內就宣判他有罪\NThe judge isn't gonna rush a conviction in less than 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.53,0:42:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們認識什麼能跟部長說上話的人嗎\NWho do we know who has the minister's ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.95,0:42:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人能夠比得過莫裏諾總統\NNobody who can trump President Moreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.39,0:42:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他對杜蘭特對人權方面的看法非常敏感\NAnd he's very sensitive to Durant's view on human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.34,0:42:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是打算放棄了嗎\NAre you giving up on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.60,0:42:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  只是現實一點\NNo. Just being realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.67,0:42:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就做莫裏諾的工作\NWork on Moreno then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.21,0:42:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們快要被人察覺了\NWe'll start leaving footprints.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.67,0:42:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點\NQuiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.83,0:42:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼\NExcuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.69,0:42:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說你  是我的鳥\NOh, not you. My birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.62,0:43:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們要做好準備\NI think we need to be prepared
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.08,0:43:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們很可能沒法把威脅進行到底了\Nfor the possibility that we can't follow through with our threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.12,0:43:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到的都是借口  不是解決方案\NI am hearing excuses, not solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.81,0:43:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無能為力\NMy hands are tied.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.60,0:43:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒法搞定整個美國國務院\NI can't circumvent the entire US State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.10,0:43:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雇你是為了讓你毀掉弗蘭克\NYou know, I hired you to destroy Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.53,0:43:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要失敗了\NYou're failing.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.31,0:43:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷蒙德  我是你的說客\NLook, Raymond, I'm your lobbyist,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.94,0:43:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的走狗\Nnot your henchman.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.74,0:43:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雇的不是說客\NI don't employ lobbyists.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.95,0:43:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雇的是對我有用的人\NI employ people who can be useful to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.82,0:43:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你看起來沒用\NAnd you are proving otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.95,0:43:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜點\NQuiet now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.89,0:43:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會想辦法的\NI'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.40,0:43:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點\NSoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.16,0:43:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行  就這樣\NOkay, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.64,0:43:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不必這麼做\NYou don't have to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.32,0:43:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我必須這麼做\NYeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.50,0:43:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指控撤銷了\NThe charges are dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.75,0:43:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們騙了你\NThey lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.63,0:43:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也可以騙他們\NYou can lie to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.78,0:43:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以提出新指控\NNew charges can always be filed.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.64,0:43:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能冒這個險\NIt's not worth the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.15,0:43:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\NOk.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.33,0:44:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你對我感到失望嗎\NAre you disappointed in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.21,0:44:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊把這事弄完吧\NLet's just get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.05,0:44:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  開始\NOK, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.14,0:44:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要做出一項聲明\NI'd like to make a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.25,0:44:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還需要一些掃尾工作\NThere will be a little cleanup,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.41,0:44:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會有一些人繼續關注這件事\Nsome folks who will want to linger on the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.99,0:44:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我們已經渡過最困難的階段了\Nbut we're over the hump, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.27,0:44:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們現在可以出門了嗎\NSo we can leave the house now?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.08,0:44:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,越快恢復正常工作越好\NThe sooner you get back to normal work, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.16,0:44:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之前被迫取消的會議\NAll the meetings I had to cancel,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.31,0:44:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想辦法再做安排\Nlet's find a way to get them back on the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.85,0:44:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.46,0:44:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得繼續推動性侵法案\NI need to push ahead with the Assault Bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.43,0:44:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們安排了明天和馬特·貝的採訪\NWe've got your Matt Bai interview lined up for tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.56,0:44:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我認為...\Nbut I think that--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.24,0:44:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們應該等事情平息之後\NMaybe we should hold off on Bai
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.14,0:44:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再考慮貝的採訪\Ntill after things quiet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.26,0:44:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛才正打算這麼說\NThat's exactly what I was gonna suggest.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.99,0:44:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道格說得對\NDoug is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.73,0:44:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  就這麼辦\NOK, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.69,0:44:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在車裏等你\NI'll meet you in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.61,0:44:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他這些事處理得很好\NHe's done a good job handling all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.66,0:44:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\NYes, he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.11,0:45:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們還要擔心什麼嗎\NShould we have any more concerns?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.21,0:45:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說他沒有別的把柄了\NHe claims he doesn't have anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.32,0:45:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信他嗎\NDo you believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.54,0:45:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到那個地步\NI wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.89,0:45:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盯著他點\NKeep an eye on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.28,0:45:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正有此意\NI plan to.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.47,0:45:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至於雷蒙德  我們快速有力地回擊\NAs for Raymond, we have to strike back hard and fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.08,0:45:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要打垮他\NI want him obliterated.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.09,0:45:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠\NMore than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.36,0:45:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓他受點折磨吧\NLet's make him suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.26,0:45:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不知我是該驕傲還是害怕\NI don't know whether to be proud or terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.53,0:45:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許兩者皆有\NPerhaps both.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.94,0:45:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我能多給你一些\NWish I could do more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.88,0:46:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算拿她做什麼\NWhat you gonna do with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.72,0:46:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒想好\NI don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.07,0:46:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許要把它拆掉\NProbably have to knock it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.74,0:46:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空地價值更高\NIt's worth more as an empty lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.73,0:46:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還有別的東西想拿走嗎\NIs there anything else you wanna take?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.07,0:46:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紀念品之類的\NA memento or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.63,0:46:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒了\NNah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.74,0:46:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是一個向後看的人\NI ain't one for lookin' back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.49,0:46:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只向前看\NEyes ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.89,0:46:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好運  弗萊迪\NGood luck, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.56,0:47:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5}{\pos(193,145)}在這一集中  弗萊迪意外成了白宮爭鬥中的一枚棋子\N在現實生活中  美國一些不知名的街邊小店\N也經常迎來總統和議員們的光顧\N2012年的總統大選開始後  奧巴馬幾乎每到一地競選\N都會在百忙中抽時間到當地聞名的餐館食坊"嘗嘗鮮"\N新罕布什爾"牛奶吧"的冰激凌  科羅拉多"辛克餐廳"的披薩\N愛荷華州"羅斯餐館"的"魔山三明治"  都被奧巴馬嘗了個遍\N他一邊走馬燈似的拉票  一邊扮演業餘美食家\N身邊的記者們也都盡職盡責地\N把總統在各地小吃  餐館中"大快朵頤"的照片傳給了全美選民
